fields.product_desc: Lightweight powder foundation that has buildable coverage and a natural matte finish. Covers imperfections and evens skin tone with a matte finish that won’t leave your skin looking flat or dry. For fuller coverage, use the included sponge and pat onto face until desired coverage is achieved. For lighter coverage, or to set foundation, sweep lightly over face with a powder brush.
This lightweight cover-up obscures imperfections discoloration and under eye circles without ever looking cakey or obvious.
Brighten up those beautiful eyes! Pencil the corners of the eyes using these vibrant brighteners for a fresh highlight.
The delicate texture of satin fused with the high color saturation creates an even finish on lips that’s long-wearing and beautiful.
The mineral-based emollient formula offers a beautiful velvet texture saturated color and it resists wear and smudging

This buttery soft, silky smooth & decadent lip gloss delivers sheer to medium coverage that melts onto your lips. It’s never sticky, always supple and kissable, plus it stays put and won't feather! Apply NYX Professional Makeup Butter Gloss with the soft doefoot applicator or Wear this lip gloss alone or glide over your favorite lipstick or lip liner to add some glossy lip shine!
NYX Pro Lip Cream Palettes feature six expertly coordinated color combinations of intensely pigmented lip creams. Wear each shade alone or blend ’em all together for a totally customized look!

A stroke of Epic Ink™ Lip Dye coats lips with a downright dramatic stain. Super-saturated and lightweight, our formula dries to a Matte finish. This stunning lip dye is an absolute makeup bag must-have. Rock it alone for an effortlessly vibrant look. Or give your favorite lippies a boost by wearing it under a similar shade!

Treat your cheeks to a radiant flush of color with our Ombré Blush, a new gradient blush inspired by the ombré trend. This must-have formula features two silky colors blended into one perfectly coordinated shade combo. (It’s like they were meant for each other.)
Inspired by the best of vintage beauty, this retro rouge covers lips in extra plush, richly pigmented and absolutely undeniable color.

A pro-level eyeshadow palette packed with 16 high-performance eyeshadows and pressed pigments in a rainbow of tone-inspired eye makeup shades. PRO-TIP - For long-lasting wear, apply an EYESHADOW PRIMER to create a smooth canvas.
